snippet.title: Vertical Dash - Android game
snippet.description:
Ever wanted a game where you just have addictive fun? Well, here it is, it doesn't matter what you are doing, this game perfectly fits the time passer's description, waiting for a friend? Playing this game will make sure that time will be used for your daily android fun!


Simple - Tap to jump, tap to dash to shown side, simple as that, yet effective!

-----
Your support and feedback is one of the top priorities! If you found any bugs, please report it to us, we will make sure its squashed. 


Any feedback is appreciated, we work hard and try to make it as positive as we can!

Contact us:

* Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/soulcrewdev/
* Twitter: https://twitter.com/SoulCrewOFCL
* Web: https://www.soulcrewdev.com
